@barbie on your Christmas tree?! Yes! Every. Single. Year.

And no, it’s not just because I’m a girly-girl who has always loved dolls…

It’s because of what Barbie represents! She represents a woman who can literally be anything that she wants. She doesn’t let anything get in the way of her dreams. 

She is a reminder that you are never too old for a fairytale or for your dream life!

This is why we call all of our clients @poshpr “Boss Dolls” and why we say the word “Doll” at all to be honest! Because no matter what you are unstoppable ✨

#dollsdoingbusiness #dollspartypretty

To everyone who told me that a pretty and pink, Barbie loving brand wouldn’t be successful… I’m doing good 😘

Step into your dream life (and business) by stepping into your 100% authentic self! Because when you stay true to yourself, you have no competition!

Cheering you on today and every single day! XoC

#dollsdoingbusiness #dollspartypretty

Unpopular opinion: candy canes and pink marshmallows in my coffee 🍬💕

But I’ve never really done what others thought was cool anyways…

I feel Ike this is my secret weapon… being able to go where no one else has gone… Completely break the mold because I am okay with being different. (Well, that and my OCD… haha I am the person who walks into the room and notices the frame in the corner of the room on the wall that needs to be adjusted by about 5 degrees to the left. I am also the person who fixes said frame! But, I digress! 💁🏼‍♀️😅)

In business you must be willing to take a chance and build a brand that completely fires up YOUR heart. And at times, this comes with a lot of unpopular opinions. 

Because how can you NOT stand out when you are being 100% authentic to YOU?!

Cheering you on today and every single day, Boss Doll! XoC #dollspartypretty #dollsdoingbusiness

I’ve talked with so many women who have the desire to create something for themselves. They tell me all about their big dreams, and I can see their face light up with excitement. 

But when I ask, “How’s that going?!” 

You wouldn’t believe how many women respond with — “Oh that’s just a dream. It won’t actually happen!” 

Do you want to know what holds most back from living the life that they’ve ACTUALLY dreamed of?

FEAR.

Fear of: failure, not being good enough, not feeling ready, judgment… you name it! 

Here’s one thing I can promise you — the woman that you look up to with the lifestyle or the business you want, it wasn’t that she didn’t feel the EXACT same fear you feel right now. It’s that she felt that fear and made a SINGLE choice. 

The choice of success. The choice thano matter what, she would make it happen. The choice that she would put everything she had into making her dream a reality.

Doll, success is a choice, and if YOU are ready to make that choice and have support in your business, head to the link in my bio…

Boss Dollars was created to help Dolls doing business build wealth and cultivate their dreams. 💰

Get yourself added to the waitlist to be the first to know ALL of the details! Link in bio! 💕

People tell me I’m a lucky girl. (And honestly, it makes me giggle!)

I was asked recently what birthday wish I made over the years that actually came true. And my answer was: ALL OF THEM.

Why would you wish for something that you don’t actually pursue? 
Why would you set a goal, and not actually work to achieve it? 
How is it possible to want something so badly and believe hard work isn’t involved? 

I might not be the smartest person in the room, but I will outwork you. And THAT is my superpower.

When someone tells me I am lucky, they underestimate how hard I work. And they definitely underestimate how much money I help female entrepreneurs make.

🤍 I want to help you find your superpower, run your business with confidence, and step into your Champagne life!

The Boss Doll Mastermind is space for you to do just this. DM me MASTERMIND and let’s chat about how we can find your superpower, together! ⚡️

I love you all so much!
